*** Context ***
+ Clear Workspace
+ A Project is created in the workspace without Execution Environment
 
*** Actions ***
- Open the main.lua file
- Declare a local variable and re-use it
- Click on the second occurence of the variable
- Right-Click -> Open Declaration
 
*** Assertions ***
# The declaration of the local variable is selected
